Come and join us tomorrow and Saturday!

Your beautiful home awaits you!

Before you step foot into the house, you’re greeted by a beautiful shaded porch. This property has three bedrooms, two and a half baths and a two car garage. There’s a warmth you feel walking through this beautiful and spacious home. The primary bedroom offers a seating area for you to kick your feet up after a long day. It also has its own bathroom equipped with both a shower and jacuzzi tub.

Love to entertain? This property comes with a beautiful backyard for festivities. It’s the perfect oasis to get away and relax. Centered in the backyard is a beautiful mimosa tree and surrounding the lawn is a wisteria bush to not only add extra zen, but more privacy. Not only do you have access to your own personal backyard oasis, but there is a basketball court, baseball field, and tennis court within the community that you can use at your own leisure.

Just got this beautiful ranch home under contract for my buyer! With one floor living, white cabinets, backsplash and some pull out cabinets in the kitchen, an en suite bathroom, two good sized bedrooms and nice rear yard with off-street parking - this home is sure to make a perfect home! Plus it's close to major roadways, Costco and the Philadelphia Premium Outlets!____________________________________________________#RealEstateSuccess #MontcoPA #HomeSweetHome
